attr.title: Kleebuu Craves Fruit Salad
attr.desc: Eat fruit, jump around, and escape the nightmares!
attr.inst: Download the KleebuuCravesFruitSalad(v1.03).zip version for free at itch.io (https://dylanbrowngames.itch.io/kleebuu-craves-fruit-salad). Extract the .zip, and copy the game files to this port's gamedata folder.
attr.inst_md: Download the *KleebuuCravesFruitSalad(v1.03).zip* version for free at [itch.io](https://dylanbrowngames.itch.io/kleebuu-craves-fruit-salad). Extract the *.zip*, and copy the game files to this port's *gamedata* folder.
